text:
──This program was brought to you
by the sponsors you see.

Asahi-chan, she's the type you just can't help but watch,
right~? I'm super curious about what she'll say next~

Being nervous
might actually be the right way to go.

Seriously, a unit live put together by Fuyu and them...
but...

Because of that middle schooler, our rehearsals
are running late, I wonder if we can really pull it off.

...Anyway, we need to make sure to meet today's goals
Setlist, staging, and then...

We need to make decisions quickly
to be able to show something perfect.

...Yeah, that's right
Might as well surprise Asahi-chan when she arrives!

If you say that, then use your head a bit
It's mostly Fuyu doing all the thinking.

Speaking of which, Asahi-chan
what's your job for today?

Supposed to be a drama shoot
I forgot where though

Gonna have some vocal and walking lessons~
What about you, Fuyuyuko-chan?
